Help Center

Delivery Rates

We deliver nationwide from $2.99 for standard shipping. Express shipping cost $6.99 and comes with tracking.

Contact us for information about international orders. We can ship as far away Canada.

Delivery Times

Back to Top

Standar shipping takes between 1 and 2 weeks. Express shipping takes 1 to 2 days.

Customer Pick Up

Back to Top

If you don't have a mail box then drop by our warehouses in Los Angeles or Atlanta.

How To Pay

Back to Top

Paying is simple. All you need is a credit card and you're good to go. We accept Master Card and visa.

About POP Shop

POP Shop is the official supplier of POP merchandise. Established in early 2016, POP Shop has an extensive supplier network that allows us to source only the best clothing, drinkware and technology for all your POP needs.

All of our items come with a 100% guarantee of authenticity and each POP item you purchase comes with a certificate to prove that you are indeed buying authentic POPware.

The POP Shop team working out of Los Angeles and Atlanta warehouses love what they do, and particularly enjoy wearing high-vis jackets and a nifty helmet.

"Working at POP Shop is okay"
Sylvester / warehouse technician
